    "description": "方块方舟的冒险者们，新的征途即将开始。让我们将探索的边界进一步延伸：在水下搭建密封仓，打造自己的秘密家园；在神秘的钴星战场对抗钴星人控制的大军，守护方舟塔，赢取丰厚奖励；改造装备，附魔套装，成为方块方舟中的顶级冒险者。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244940/extras/cd3dbe4a6f37ced9da1cfa9b077e4a9e.avif?t=1671783926\" width=610 height=334 /></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >水下建筑体系</h2></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244940/extras/e4166e0cf691b492e06cfe4a7d0cb2ea.avif?t=1671783926\" width=610 height=334 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244940/extras/230426a8946173c49a46b6985b16180c.poster.avif?t=1671783926\" width=350 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244940/extras/230426a8946173c49a46b6985b16180c.webm?t=1671783926\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244940/extras/230426a8946173c49a46b6985b16180c.mp4?t=1671783926\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>通过月池舱与密封舱，在水下构建出一片隔绝水体的建筑空间，打造隐蔽而舒适的水下家园。</li></ul>从全新的水下视角开启冒险，游览并改造独特的水下环境；<br>采用舱体模块化搭建，自由构筑你的水下家园；<br>可在水下建筑放置近200种家具，风格随心切换；<br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >守护方舟塔</h2></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244940/extras/5f7713a5841aeceef8d9e416a53225f8.avif?t=1671783926\" width=800 height=250 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>贪婪的钴星人再一次开始了掠夺，带上强力的生物伙伴，一起守护方舟塔，对抗钴星人控制的怪物，赢取丰厚奖励。</li></ul>魔法岛、冰火岛、钴星战场三大全新关卡场景<br>带上最强力的生物伙伴，激战兽潮与外星机器人<br>通关奖励爆满地，赢取蓝图、全新套装、改造材料等稀有奖励<br><strong>守护方舟传送器，需要玩家免费激活水之屋版本后，在精致建筑小屋中制作获取</strong><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >装备改造与附魔</h2></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244940/extras/3c81a67a62d8dded843583f882b04001.avif?t=1671783926\" width=610 height=342 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244940/extras/8500a660449975abd5404ee3cd7f561e.avif?t=1671783926\" width=610 height=342 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>提升实力是冒险中不可或缺的一环，用新的战利品改造装备、附魔套装，以更加强大的姿态迎接挑战。</li></ul>“枪械改造台”升级为“装备改造台”<br>改造装备获取额外属性，外观也会随之发生变化<br>消耗元素结晶附魔装备，形成元素套装解锁新词条",
